{"tid":1396570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[注意] 唔好再理Trump 對香港及中國既言論，要冷處理","createTime":"2019-08-02T06:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:10:00.000Z","uid":275507,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"da0313c0a092811f2b5247764911f0a05c85615a","tid":1396570,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:45:06.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得 Trump 每日次講既說話，你都唔會知佢背後既動作。<br />\n<br />\n佢對北韓展現強硬態度 ＝》 過幾個月可以同金正恩會面<br />\n佢同金正恩話做Friend ＝》 過幾個月可以談判破裂<br />\n佢話同習近平做好朋友 ＝》加關稅<br />\n佢話會重啟談判 ＝》傾幾個月都未開始<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今次對港言論 ＝》額外加10%開稅</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極度懷疑呢幾日幾Trump 對香港既言論無限放大既人係為左擾亂人心，有了解時事既人根本知道Trump 講人處事反覆無常無從估計。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d655699ca36f51b35e97fd4c2e00d125f915e98d","tid":1396570,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d45bd461389ccd7cd7ac33c9a4843999a0dbb3a","tid":1396570,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c259beed61b51dba2f10747cfd48f230af3001","tid":1396570,"uid":59922,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"侵講嘢不嬲白宮見記者一套，夜晚返屋企上Twitter又另一套啦<br />\n彈出又彈入"},{"pid":"2ce7add13b1d7cfa567af0cb24cdb76abb5835e5","tid":1396570,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:54:47.000Z","msg":"其實大家唔駛對trump有咩期望 做返好自己野 佢適時助攻當bonus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c9e03b9bbe244da6a1eaea3ff5f5eed2811beb","tid":1396570,"uid":275507,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ce7add13b1d7cfa567af0cb24cdb76abb5835e5","tid":1396570,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:54:47.000Z","msg":"其